## Optional: override default image tags and commands.
## Copy to .env.local to customize.
## AIRBYTE_BASE_IMAGE defaults to the CDK version bundled with the deployed
## Airbyte platform (see BASE_IMAGE comment in source.sh) — do NOT use :latest,
## its strict schema drifts ahead of the deployed Builder UI.
# AIRBYTE_CONNECTOR_IMAGE=airbyte/source-declarative-manifest:local-6.60.9
# AIRBYTE_BASE_IMAGE=airbyte/source-declarative-manifest:6.60.9
# AIRBYTE_COMMAND=source-declarative-manifest
# AIRBYTE_SECRETS_TMPFS_OPTS=/secrets:rw,mode=1777
